<div class="container grid grid--2-cols grid--center-v">

    <div class="step-text-box">
        <p class="step-number">01</p>
        <h3 class="heading-tertiary">Set up your recruiter profile</h3>
        <p class="step-description">
            Join the platform by selecting the <strong>Recruiter</strong> role during registration. This gives you full access to our talent management dashboard, where you can start building your company's presence and sourcing the right candidates.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="step-img-box">
        <img src="~/Img/Recruiter-Account-Creation.png" class="step-img" />
    </div>

    <div class="step-img-box">
        <img src="~/Img/Recruiter-Jobs-Dashboard.png" class="step-img" />
    </div>
    <div class="step-text-box">
        <p class="step-number">02</p>
        <h3 class="heading-tertiary">Manage your job portfolio</h3>
        <p class="step-description">
            Your dashboard is the command center for your hiring pipeline. View, edit, or delete existing job posts, and dive directly into candidate applications for any specific role with a single click.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="step-text-box">
        <p class="step-number">03</p>
        <h3 class="heading-tertiary">Define precision job requirements</h3>
        <p class="step-description">
            Create highly detailed job listings. Beyond standard descriptions, you can attach specific <strong>required skills and proficiency levels</strong>, ensuring that the AI only presents you with candidates who truly fit your needs.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="step-img-box">
        <img src="~/Img/Recruiter-Add-Job.png" class="step-img" />
    </div>

    <div class="step-img-box">
        <img src="~/Img/Recruiter-Add-Quiz.png" class="step-img" />
    </div>
    <div class="step-text-box">
        <p class="step-number">04</p>
        <h3 class="heading-tertiary">Validate skills with custom quizzes</h3>
        <p class="step-description">
            Go beyond the resume. Attach custom-built quizzes to your job posts to directly test a candidate's practical knowledge, giving you objective data on their skill levels before you even interview them.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="step-text-box">
        <p class="step-number">05</p>
        <h3 class="heading-tertiary">Review ranked applications</h3>
        <p class="step-description">
            See your applicants sorted by <strong>Match Score</strong>. Analyze their background, quiz results, and how well their skills align with your requirements. We bring the best talent to the top of your list.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="step-img-box">
        <img src="~/Img/Recruiter-Applications-View.png" class="step-img" />
    </div>
</div>